    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
<span rend="jisage_1" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em">
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鋼</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はがね</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の波に<lb />
　　アベラール沈み<lb />
鉛の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">艫</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">とも</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<lb />
　　エロイーズ浮む<lb />
</span>
<lb />
骸炭は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">澪</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">みを</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に乗り<lb />
直立する彼岸花を捧げて走り<lb />
『死』は半ば<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">脣</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を開いて　水を恋ひ<lb />
また　<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">燠</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">霊床</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たまどこ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>とする<lb />
すべては　緑礬のみづ底に息をつく<lb />
象牙<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">球</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">だま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の腹部の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">内</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うちら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>側に<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
